Interface InputNotifier<T extends InputHandler>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of handlers
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Processor, Reader
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractInputNotifier, AbstractProcessor, AbstractReader, AbstractXmiReader, EcoreProcessor, PersistenceNotifier, XmiStreamReader, XPathProcessor

    public interface InputNotifier<T extends InputHandler>
    An object that notifies registered InputHandlers of events during an I/O process, such as import or export.
    See Also:
    InputHandler
